00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:04.720
We call it direct meritocracy because&nbsp;
we do have voted representatives but&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:08.240
you don't have to give them your merits&nbsp;
the voting power of your merits. You can&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:16.720
give it to them but you can also always work&nbsp;
directly with your shares whenever you like.

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:21.600
What is the future for cities? Do you want to&nbsp;
